description: The latest wave of Warhammer 40,000: Kill Team releases brings exciting new options for fans of tactical skirmish battles. At the forefront is the new expansion Kill Team: Brutal and Cunning, introducing a tense conflict between the Ork Wrecka Krew and a team of sharp-eyed Ratlings. Set in the treacherous Undermuzzle Barrens, this expansion offers...
title: Kill Team: Brutal and Cunning Leads a Packed Week of Warhammer Releases
